Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:02.92,Staff,NTP,0,0,0,,字幕来源：动音漫影 & 极影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:04.88,Staff,NTP,0,0,0,,片源：R2JRAW  翻译：荷伊 & SS  后期：kenan2763
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.71,0:00:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来比起石原狠毒的棍子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是你们的软拳头比较好受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.76,0:00:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...我才一直乖乖挨打的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们...做得过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离出所还有三周
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱木的怒火爆发了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么想死的话 那就如你所愿打死你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来今夜似乎就能解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天您得来这边一趟 开一份死亡诊断书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中的石头终于可以放下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 石原君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何了？之前跟你说的那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指横须贺丈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你快点哦 我可是很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.53,0:02:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 早上的点名...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,横山！发生了什么事 快告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事...都没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！？你在说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被樱木打的 对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...只是我们几个伙伴之间发生了点争执
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和樱木...没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我说实话！你们不都是被樱木打的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想反抗我吗 混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太得意忘行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石原先生...请饶了...我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！可恶！可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱木...饶不了你...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理雄 对不起 很疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蚂蚱会跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟也能飞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我们却连梦想也不配拥有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法活着走出特少的高墙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱木凝望着自己内心的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水上 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也...觉得石原先生对樱木的惩处很不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...我先回院里了 你好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 真理雄那家伙到底出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然间就被送去了医院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是熊谷带他去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之现在只能等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先回去吧 不然会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:06:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你脸色似乎有点不好啊 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会是感冒了吧 有发烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我没觉得不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得你是横须贺丈君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丈 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎你随时来医务室玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见他那眼神了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他盯上丈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么大冷的天 你们在外面干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呦 好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有三周 樱木就出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来 石原老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被打也忍着 不受挑衅 也不违反规定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底该怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很简单 只要引他违反就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引他违反？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱木为了自己是不会违反规定的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了自己的话 呐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理雄的拳头被砸碎了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会被送到医院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我 都怪我一直责备真理雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能只怪你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再跟我牵扯上关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需要再忍耐三周
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我会在外面等着你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在偷偷摸摸地说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们先回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连个招呼都不和我打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说莫非...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不负责你们监舍 你们就不跟我打招呼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整列！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立正！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:08:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬礼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听话就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你们抬起头来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我叫你们抬起头之前 保持弯腰姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别给我动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 是这么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想让我们受苦...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑衅阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子 尽用些卑鄙手段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就撑给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石原先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下这么大雨 你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我闭上嘴看着 熊谷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱木 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恨我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以一拳向我挥过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙们到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人可支撑不了五分钟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 石原先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算叫我们抬起身来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说因为在雨里受了凉 肚子疼起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 谁让你们说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这手是什么意思 樱木
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然对看守动手 你应该知道会有什么下场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然这样乱来...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年们流出的泪水 与雨一同渗入了地面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲痛和仇恨...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却刻印在心底 永远无法消却
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呦 樱木 吃晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听不到吗 吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？没有食欲？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能放你出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你手上捏着我们的把柄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:13:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年以前 二舍六房里收容着两位少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为伤害案件入所的樱木六郎太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有因为抢劫未遂入所的荻野荣一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人因为年纪相同 很快就混熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要去抢劫？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊 没有其他路可走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然让我到哪去弄老妈的住院费啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住院？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老妈 已经病得很重了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是没有钱让她住院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道让我就这样等着老妈病死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样 就别轻易被人抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不陪着你妈怎么行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要考虑尽快出所就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荻野 佐佐木要对你进行结核病的再检查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石原老师 荻野上周应该也检查过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱木 我去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收好了 那么请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我会的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次 不是说了是最后一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想快点见到妈妈吗 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 这样可以让我快点出所了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说好的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为那么容易就能出得去啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 你还是乖乖地听佐佐木医生的话比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...好像能比原来想得更早见到老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石原收了钱 把我带给佐佐木做玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连说让我早点出所的约定他们也不遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去天国等老妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荻野...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果 荻野荣一的死被作为事故处理了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然说这种话 樱木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:17:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你和佐佐木逼死荻野的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是自杀 是被你们杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 不管怎么样吧 已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你不可能出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥他...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被关禁闭以后 就没有让他吃过饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？那以来已经一周了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算就这样不闻不问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要对阿哥见死不救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是打算做些什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是和那个石原一样不把我们当人看的看守
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定会救出阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 一次都没给他吃过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按佐佐木医生的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人两周不吃不喝是没法活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那死亡诊断书就写衰弱引起的急性心力衰竭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人...想杀掉樱木...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卷心菜...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想什么 我们早看透了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荻野 我快要挺不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下可以过去跟你道个歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 躲到什么地方了 那个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,元鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你还没死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直没吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...就为了这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太简单了 看守都是一群废物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天晚饭有醃萝卜 我给你包在里边了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 阿哥 好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么好吃的饭团 我还是第一次吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.48,0:20:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荻野 我还不能到你那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这边还有我宝贵的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是群不可救药的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过都是我可爱的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想继续和他们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对一个个同伴的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:21:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唤醒了阿哥活下去的力量和继续战斗的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荻野 我来为你血洗冤仇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱木再次起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱的水刑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.47,0:22:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六人下定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不让阿哥死掉
